# Gestalt-System-Monitor — example local config.
#
# Copy to `.env.local` (gitignored) and fill in machine-specific values. Values
# already set in the real environment win over this file. NOTHING here should
# contain a private path — keep real install paths only in your own .env.local.

# --- Web dev server: which agent to spawn alongside `npm run dev` --------------
# unset  => real LAN discovery + launcher (default)
# --mock => synthesize a fake LAN (beacons + feeds) for front-end work
# off    => don't spawn an agent (you run it yourself)
# GSM_AGENT=--mock

# --- Launch profile: how the agent launches matches ---------------------------
# standalone  : an editor-built standalone game exe (recommended for local dev;
#               full agent-managed autosave). Requires GSM_STANDALONE_EXE.
# ue          : UnrealEditor.exe + a .uproject (-game). Requires GSM_UE_EXE + GSM_UE_PROJECT.
# (unset)     : discover a Steam install; launching needs GSM_HEADLESS_ARGS or a profile.
# GSM_HEADLESS_PROFILE=standalone

# --- Standalone profile -------------------------------------------------------
# GSM_STANDALONE_EXE=C:\path\to\YourBuild\Binaries\Win64\YourGame.exe
# GSM_STANDALONE_CWD=C:\path\to\YourBuild\Binaries\Win64
# WS-port fallback for single (non-autosave) dev matches: the game's default log.
# GSM_STANDALONE_LOG=C:\path\to\Project\Saved\Logs\YourGame.log

# --- UE profile (editor + uproject) -------------------------------------------
# GSM_UE_EXE=C:\path\to\Engine\Binaries\Win64\UnrealEditor.exe
# GSM_UE_PROJECT=C:\path\to\Project\YourGame.uproject

# --- Headless match knobs (optional) ------------------------------------------
# unset render => nullrhi (headless, best for batches). 'windowed' to watch a match;
# 'offscreen' for headless-with-RHI.
# GSM_HEADLESS_RENDER=windowed
# GSM_HEADLESS_MAP_ID=9
# GSM_HEADLESS_MATCH_INTERVAL_SEC=5
# GSM_HEADLESS_ATTR_RECORD=1
# GSM_HEADLESS_ATTR_HZ=10

# --- Steam discovery overrides (optional) -------------------------------------
# GSM_GAME_NAME=Gestalt System
# GSM_STEAM_APP_ID=
# GSM_GAME_DIR=
# GSM_GAME_EXE=

# --- Trace replay (optional) --------------------------------------------------
# GSM_TRACE_DIR=
# GSM_TRACE_DIRS=traces/multi-15
# GSM_TRACE_LOOP=1
